WEBVTT

19:01.275 --> 19:02.525
That is why I came here myself.

19:02.775 --> 19:04.775
Even if you confess that
you are Pattampoochi...

19:04.942 --> 19:05.984
The law and order needs to know...

19:06.025 --> 19:08.192
Motive - The reason behind the murders

19:08.317 --> 19:10.442
Modus Operandi - How did you murder?

19:11.109 --> 19:13.942
Material Evidence - The weapon used
to commit the murder.

19:14.234 --> 19:15.484
These three M's are required.

19:16.067 --> 19:17.859
To find them out, we
should definitely talk.

19:18.025 --> 19:18.734
So talk.

19:19.650 --> 19:21.192
I don't talk to fools.

19:24.067 --> 19:24.692
But I do.

19:25.067 --> 19:25.817
So, tell me.

19:25.984 --> 19:26.984
Sarcasm?

19:27.067 --> 19:29.484
You chickened out when few
reporters asked you questions.

19:29.942 --> 19:31.817
Now if I tell you all
that I have done...
